data.description: A charming residence nestled in the heart of Glendale. This inviting home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style, making it an ideal haven for modern living. With 3006 square feet, you will have plenty of room to entertain guest. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a well-maintained exterior and attractive landscaping, creating a warm and welcoming curb appeal. Step inside, and you'll discover a thoughtfully designed interior that seamlessly combines functionality with aesthetic appeal. Venture outside to the backyard, where you'll find a peaceful retreat perfect for enjoying the Arizona sunshine. Whether you're entertaining guests or simply unwinding after a long day, the outdoor space provides a versatile setting for all your leisure activities.
